---
import LandingLayout from '../layouts/LandingLayout.astro';

const brand = import.meta.env.PUBLIC_BRAND;
const isJCL = brand === 'jason-c-lewis';
---

{isJCL ? (
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>Operator's Log — Jason C. Lewis</title>
<meta name="description" content="Practical AI perspective from someone who's been building and advising for 14 years. Weekly newsletter from the operator's seat." />
<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Audiowide&family=Chakra+Petch:wght@400;500;600&family=Orbitron:wght@600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
<style>
/* ============================================================
   DESIGN TOKENS
   ============================================================ */
:root {
  --bg-primary: #fafaf8;
  --bg-alt: #f2f2ee;
  --bg-card: #ffffff;
  --bg-dark: #111113;
  --bg-dark-card: #1a1a1c;
  --bg-dark-subtle: #222225;
  --text-primary: #1a1a1a;
  --text-body: #3a3a3a;
  --text-muted: #71716b;
  --text-faint: #a1a19b;
  --text-on-dark: #f5f5f0;
  --text-body-dark: #b8b8b0;
  --text-muted-dark: #888880;
  --text-faint-dark: #555558;
  --accent: #c1d42f;
  --accent-hover: #d4e635;
  --accent-pressed: #a8b828;
  --accent-tint: rgba(193, 212, 47, 0.09);
  --accent-glow: rgba(193, 212, 47, 0.19);
  --cta-text: #111113;
  --border: #e2e2de;
  --border-hover: #c1d42f;
  --border-dark: #333335;
  --max-content: 1120px;
  --max-narrow: 720px;
  --max-cards: 1040px;
  --max-twocol: 880px;
}

/* ============================================================
   RESET & BASE
   ============================================================ */
*, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
html { scroll-behavior: smooth; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; }
body {
  background: var(--bg-primary);
  color: var(--text-body);
  font-family: 'Chakra Petch', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
  font-size: 17px;
  line-height: 1.7;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
}
img { max-width: 100%; display: block; }
a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }

/* ============================================================
   NAVIGATION
   ============================================================ */
.nav {
  position: sticky;
  top: 0;
  z-index: 100;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  height: 64px;
  padding: 0 64px;
  background: transparent;
  transition: background 0.3s ease;
}
.nav.on-dark .nav-brand { color: var(--text-on-dark); }
.nav.scrolled {
  background: rgba(250, 250, 248, 0.9);
  backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}
.nav.scrolled .nav-brand { color: var(--text-primary); }
.nav-brand {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
  font-family: 'Audiowide', system-ui, sans-serif;
  font-size: 18px;
  line-height: 1.15;
  letter-spacing: 0.11em;
  color: var(--text-primary);
  transition: color 0.3s ease;
}
.nav-brand-bar {
  display: block;
  width: 3px;
  height: 20px;
  background: var(--accent);
  border-radius: 2px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.nav-cta {
  padding: 8px 20px;
  border-radius: 6px;
  background: var(--accent);
  color: var(--cta-text);
  font-family: 'Chakra Petch', system-ui, sans-serif;
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: background 0.15s ease, transform 0.15s ease;
}
.nav-cta:hover { background: var(--accent-hover); transform: scale(1.02); }

/* ============================================================
   HERO
   ============================================================ */
.hero {
  background: var(--bg-dark);
  padding: 140px 64px 120px;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.hero-inner {
  max-width: var(--max-content);
  margin: 0 auto;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 3fr 2fr;
  gap: 60px;
  align-items: center;
}
.hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 2; }
.credential-pill {
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 6px 16px;
  border: 1px solid var(--border-dark);
  border-radius: 20px;
  font-family: 'Audiowide', system-ui, sans-serif;
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--text-muted-dark);
  margin-bottom: 32px;
}
.hero h1 {
  font-family: 'Orbitron', system-ui, sans-serif;
  font-size: 56px;
  font-weight: 700;
  line-height: 1.05;
  letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  color: var(--text-on-dark);
  margin-bottom: 24px;
}
.hero h1 .accent { color: var(--accent); }
.hero-sub {
  font-family: 'Chakra Petch', system-ui, sans-serif;
  font-size: 20px;
  line-height: 1.6;
  color: var(--text-muted-dark);
  max-width: 540px;
  margin-bottom: 40px;
}
.hero-form { display: flex; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
.hero-input {
  width: 320px;
  padding: 14px 18px;
  background: var(--bg-dark-card);
  border: 1px solid var(--border-dark);
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-family: 'Chakra Petch', system-ui, sans-serif;
  font-size: 16px;
  color: var(--text-on-dark);
  outline: none;
  transition: border-color 0.15s ease;
}
.hero-input::placeholder { color: var(--text-faint-dark); }
.hero-input:focus { border-color: var(--accent); }
.btn-primary {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  padding: 14px 32px;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 8px;
  background: var(--accent);
  color: var(--cta-text);
  font-family: 'Chakra Petch', system-ui, sans-serif;
  font-size: 16px;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: background 0.15s ease, transform 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease;
  white-space: nowrap;
}
.btn-primary:hover { background: var(--accent-hover); transform: scale(1.02); box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(193, 212, 47, 0.25); }
.btn-primary:active { background: var(--accent-pressed); transform: scale(0.98); }
.btn-primary:disabled { opacity: 0.6; cursor: not-allowed; transform: none; }
.hero-micro { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; color: var(--text-faint-dark); }
.hero-form-success {
  display: none;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
  font-size: 15px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--accent);
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.hero-form-success.show { display: flex; }
.hero-headshot {
  width: 380px;
  aspect-ratio: 3/4;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a1c 0%, #222225 100%);
  border-radius: 16px;
  border: 2px solid var(--accent-glow);
  box-shadow: 0 0 60px var(--accent-glow);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.hero-headshot img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  border-radius: 14px;
}

/* ============================================================
   SECTIONS
   ============================================================ */
.section { padding: 120px 64px; }
.section-white { background: var(--bg-card); }
.section-alt { background: var(--bg-alt); }
.section-inner { max-width: var(--max-content); margin: 0 auto; }
.section-inner.narrow { max-width: var(--max-narrow); }
.section-pill {
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 4px 14px;
  border: 1px solid var(--accent);
  border-radius: 20px;
  font-family: 'Audiowide', system-ui, sans-serif;
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--accent);
  margin-bottom: 32px;
}
h2 {
  font-family: 'Orbitron', system-ui, sans-serif;
  font-size: 36px;
  font-weight: 600;
  line-height: 1.15;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  color: var(--text-primary);
}
h2.on-dark { color: var(--text-on-dark); }
h2 .accent { color: var(--accent); }
.section-sub { font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--text-muted); }
.text-center { text-align: center; }

/* Problem */
.problem-body { max-width: 640px; margin: 48px auto 0; text-align: left; }
.problem-body p { margin-bottom: 24px; color: var(--text-body); }
.problem-body p:last-child { color: var(--text-primary); font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 0; }

/* Cards */
.card-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 24px; max-width: var(--max-cards); margin: 0 auto; }
.card {
  background: var(--bg-card);
  border: 1px solid var(--border);
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 32px;
  transition: border-color 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
}
.card:hover { border-color: var(--accent); transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.04); }
.card-icon {
  width: 44px; height: 44px;
  background: var(--accent-tint);
  border-radius: 10px;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.card-icon svg { width: 24px; height: 24px; stroke: var(--accent); stroke-width: 1.5; fill: none; }
h3 {
  font-family: 'Orbitron', system-ui, sans-serif;
  font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.3;
  letter-spacing: -0.01em; color: var(--text-primary);
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}
.card p { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.65; color: var(--text-body); }

/* Career */
.career-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 32px; }
.career-block { border-left: 3px solid var(--accent); padding-left: 24px; }
.career-label { font-family: 'Audiowide', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 8px; }
.career-title { font-family: 'Orbitron', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.3; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 12px; }
.career-body { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--text-body); margin-bottom: 16px; }
.career-metric { display: inline-block; font-family: 'Orbitron', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-primary); background: var(--accent-tint); padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 6px; }
.section-divider { width: 80px; height: 2px; background: var(--accent); margin: 64px auto; border-radius: 1px; }

/* Samples */
.sample-header { font-family: 'Orbitron', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-primary); text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px; }
.sample-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 32px; }
.sample-card { background: #f8f8f5; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 32px; }
.sample-label { font-family: 'Audiowide', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 16px; }
.sample-title { font-family: 'Orbitron', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.3; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 12px; }
.sample-body { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--text-body); }
.sample-placeholder { background: var(--bg-alt); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; padding: 40px; text-align: center; color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 14px; margin-top: 16px; }

/* Differentiation */
.diff-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 48px; max-width: var(--max-twocol); margin: 0 auto; }
.diff-card { background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 36px; }
.diff-header { font-family: 'Audiowide', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase; padding-bottom: 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); margin-bottom: 24px; }
.diff-header.positive { color: var(--accent); }
.diff-header.negative { color: var(--text-muted); }
.diff-list { list-style: none; }
.diff-list li { position: relative; padding-left: 28px; margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--text-body); }
.diff-list li:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
.diff-list li .marker { position: absolute; left: 0; font-weight: 700; }
.diff-list.positive li .marker { color: var(--accent); }
.diff-list.negative li .marker { color: var(--text-faint); }
.diff-list.negative li { color: var(--text-muted); }

/* FAQ */
.faq-list { max-width: var(--max-narrow); margin: 0 auto; }
.faq-item { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
.faq-item:first-child { border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
.faq-item summary { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 24px 0; cursor: pointer; font-family: 'Chakra Petch', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-primary); list-style: none; user-select: none; }
.faq-item summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
.faq-chevron { width: 16px; height: 16px; stroke: var(--text-muted); stroke-width: 2; fill: none; flex-shrink: 0; margin-left: 16px; transition: transform 0.2s ease; }
.faq-item[open] .faq-chevron { transform: rotate(90deg); }
.faq-answer { padding: 0 0 24px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--text-body); }

/* Final CTA */
.final-cta { background: var(--bg-dark); padding: 120px 64px; text-align: center; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
.final-cta-inner { position: relative; z-index: 2; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }
.final-cta h2 { font-size: 40px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px; }
.final-cta .section-sub { color: var(--text-muted-dark); letter-spacing: 0.02em; margin-bottom: 40px; }
.final-form { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
.final-input { width: 360px; padding: 14px 18px; background: var(--bg-dark-card); border: 1px solid var(--border-dark); border-radius: 8px; font-family: 'Chakra Petch', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; color: var(--text-on-dark); outline: none; transition: border-color 0.15s ease; }
.final-input::placeholder { color: var(--text-faint-dark); }
.final-input:focus { border-color: var(--accent); }
.final-micro { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; color: var(--text-faint-dark); margin-bottom: 24px; }
.final-form-success {
  display: none;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 10px;
  font-size: 15px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--accent);
  margin-bottom: 16px;
}
.final-form-success.show { display: flex; }
.link-secondary { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text-muted-dark); transition: color 0.15s ease; }
.link-secondary:hover { color: var(--accent); }
.link-secondary .arrow { display: inline-block; transition: transform 0.15s ease; }
.link-secondary:hover .arrow { transform: translateX(4px); }

/* Footer */
.footer { background: var(--bg-dark); padding: 40px 64px; border-top: 1px solid var(--bg-dark-subtle); display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
.footer-brand { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; font-family: 'Audiowide', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.11em; color: #71716b; }
.footer-right { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; }
.footer-social svg { width: 20px; height: 20px; stroke: var(--text-faint-dark); fill: none; stroke-width: 1.5; transition: stroke 0.15s ease; }
.footer-social:hover svg { stroke: var(--accent); }
.footer-copy { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-faint-dark); }

/* ============================================================
   RESPONSIVE
   ============================================================ */
@media (max-width: 767px) {
  .nav { padding: 0 20px; }
  .hero { padding: 100px 20px 80px; }
  .hero-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
  .hero h1 { font-size: 36px; }
  .hero-sub { font-size: 17px; }
  .hero-form { flex-direction: column; }
  .hero-input { width: 100%; }
  .btn-primary { width: 100%; justify-content: center; }
  .hero-headshot { width: 280px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .section { padding: 80px 20px; }
  h2 { font-size: 28px; }
  .card-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 16px; }
  .career-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .sample-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .diff-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 24px; }
  .final-cta { padding: 80px 20px; }
  .final-cta h2 { font-size: 28px; }
  .final-form { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
  .final-input { width: 100%; }
  .final-form .btn-primary { width: 100%; }
  .footer { flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; text-align: center; padding: 32px 20px; }
}

.mb-16 { margin-bottom: 16px; }
.mb-48 { margin-bottom: 48px; }
.mb-56 { margin-bottom: 56px; }
</style>
</head>

<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav class="nav on-dark" id="mainNav">
  <a href="#" class="nav-brand"><span class="nav-brand-bar"></span>jasonclewis</a>
  <button class="nav-cta" onclick="document.getElementById('heroEmailInput').focus(); document.getElementById('heroSection').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">Subscribe</button>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero" id="heroSection">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="credential-pill">Former Gartner Analyst &middot; Head of AWS Startups NA</div>
      <h1>Fourteen years in AI. Here's what I'm learning from <span class="accent">the trenches.</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Every week I share what I'm actually seeing — what's working, what's overhyped, and where I'd focus if I were making your decisions. Grounded in real operator experience at AWS and Gartner. Practical by design.</p>
      <div class="hero-form" id="heroFormWrap">
        <input type="email" class="hero-input" id="heroEmailInput" placeholder="Your best email" aria-label="Email address" />
        <button class="btn-primary" id="heroSubmitBtn" onclick="handleSubscribe('heroEmailInput','heroFormWrap','heroSuccess','heroSubmitBtn')">Subscribe to Operator's Log</button>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-form-success" id="heroSuccess">
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
        You're on the list. First issue coming soon.
      </div>
      <p class="hero-micro">Free. Weekly. 5-minute read. Unsubscribe anytime.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-headshot" role="img" aria-label="Jason C. Lewis">
      <img src="/images/jason_tie.png" alt="Jason C. Lewis professional headshot" onerror="this.parentElement.style.background='linear-gradient(135deg,#1a1a1c 0%,#222225 100%)'" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHY THIS EXISTS -->
<section class="section section-white">
  <div class="section-inner narrow text-center">
    <div class="section-pill">Why This Exists</div>
    <h2>AI is moving fast. Knowing what actually matters for your business is genuinely hard.</h2>
    <div class="problem-body">
      <p>Every week there's a new model, a new framework, a new capability being called a game-changer. Some of it is. Most of it needs context before you know how to respond. The signal-to-noise ratio is rough right now.</p>
      <p>I've spent 14 years in roles where I had to know the difference — advising organizations at Gartner, supporting the fastest-scaling AI startups at AWS, and building products myself. I've seen what works in production and what looks good in a demo.</p>
      <p>Operator's Log is my attempt to share that perspective. Not the loudest take. Not a vendor pitch. Just honest, grounded observations from someone who's been accountable for real AI outcomes — and is still in the middle of it.</p>
      <p>If you're making real decisions about AI — for your team, your product, or your career — I hope it's useful.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHAT YOU GET -->
<section class="section section-alt">
  <div class="section-inner text-center">
    <div class="section-pill">What You Get</div>
    <h2 class="mb-16">One email. Every week. Practical AI perspective from the operator's seat.</h2>
    <p class="section-sub mb-56">Here's what you'll find in every edition of Operator's Log.</p>
    <div class="card-grid">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="6"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="2"/><line x1="12" y1="2" x2="12" y2="4"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="22"/><line x1="2" y1="12" x2="4" y2="12"/><line x1="20" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12"/></svg></div>
        <h3>What's Actually Working</h3>
        <p>I lead support for the fastest-scaling AI startups in North America. I see which AI approaches ship to production and which die in pilot. You get that intel weekly, without the vendor spin.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polygon points="16.24 7.76 14.12 14.12 7.76 16.24 9.88 9.88 16.24 7.76"/></svg></div>
        <h3>What to Bet On Next</h3>
        <p>Every week surfaces a new "must-have" AI capability. Most are noise. I tell you which ones are worth your time, your budget, and your team's attention. Grounded in patterns across 14,000+ organizations.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/></svg></div>
        <h3>How to Build With It</h3>
        <p>Not theory. I'm a full-stack developer shipping AI-powered products right now. The newsletter covers what works in production, what breaks at scale, and what the demos conveniently leave out.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHY LISTEN -->
<section class="section section-white">
  <div class="section-inner text-center">
    <div class="section-pill">Why Listen</div>
    <h2 class="mb-56">This isn't a side project. It's 14 years of operating leverage.</h2>
    <div class="career-grid">
